The fastest method present in String class in JAVA to convert charArray to String is the static method of String class
called valueOf(charArray[]).

Source: http://stackoverflow.com/questions/7655127/how-to-convert-a-char-array-back-to-a-string-java

PLEASE DO REMEMBER THIS

Example: 
public static String sortString(String s){
	char[] array = s.toCharArray();
	Arrays.sort(array);
	return String.valueOf(array);   // convert char array to String
}
